section.heading: Metropolitan Police Department community policing working group.

annotations.annotation: Applicability of D.C. Law 21-125: § 901 of D.C. Law 21-125 provided that the change made to this section by § 201 of D.C. Law 21-125 is subject to the inclusion of the law’s fiscal effect in an approved budget and financial plan. Therefore the change made to this section by that amendment has been delayed.
